\begin_layout Subsection*

\lang english
1.
 Purpose
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\lang english
This policy establishes the authorization decision process by which the IT Director,
 as the designated Authorizing Official,
 reviews security control assessment results and renders formal authorization decisions for County information systems and controls governed by the ECIO Policy Manual.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection*

\lang english
2.
